phrases: All of a sudden, I was there.
My parents went into the dungeon to make money,
You are cutting into my profits!
Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon?
It is been so long since I have had any Soma!
you say that it is not their god that the Soma Familia worships,
This insanely expensive stuff is, to them, a failure.
What they worship is the perfected stuff, which they will not sell to anybody.
One sip can get you wasted, to the bottom of your soul.
All the children of the Soma Familia are only there to drink it.
That is all the Soma Familia is?
It takes money to really focus on brewing.
The ones who make a lot of money get a little drink of the perfect stuff.
And once you have had it, you want it again,
so you are desperate for cash.
You will take every valis you can get,
even if it means screwing your companions,
Well, that is about all I know.
How long are you going to be glum,
just because your man ran off on you?
I will touch your soft skin all over!
If you do anything weird, I will stab you.
She is an interesting goddess, is not she?
Interesting or not, she is far sharper than she looks.
Even if it means sacrificing others, huh?
I see.. it is that supporter, huh?
It looks like there are bad adventurers after her.
I was hoping we could let her stay here for a while.
It is a bad thing to say, but I have to say it.
Did you really lose your knife?
It is the same with those adventurers who were attacking her.
She is hiding something from you.
Do you want to go there today?
You are strong enough to do it!
But I only survived the seventh floor because of your magic weapon...
And starting on the tenth floor...
As strong as you are now, you will not have any problems!
Like that magic you showed me yesterday!
I have been down to the eleventh floor, and I guarantee it.
I was planning on talking to Hestia soon,
but I did not think I would be asked to do the Babel inspection.
I should not involve my job with my personal life,
but it is for the best, right?
I need to talk to her about Bell-kun's supporter.
Thank you for agreeing to my plan!
I am really lucky to be a supporter for someone like you!
I guess have to go to the tenth floor at some point.
This is not really my place to say anything, but...
Why not use this from now on?
does not quite have the reach needed to fight a large monster.
I saved the adventurer you are in charge of?
I have been wanting to thank you.
I heard you saved him at the last second from a raging minotaur
He is very grateful to you for saving him!
So the white-haired kid is about to get set up for a fall by Arde?
And you know what will happen then.
Do not screw it up, you guys.
Miss Wallenstein, I am aware that this is rude,
but may I ask you a favor?
So this is the tenth floor?
This is our goal for today.
It is dangerous, so stay close, Lili.
But it looks like you do not have time to cut them all down.
If I cannot beat an orc,
I will never beat the monsters that come after this!
What are you thinking, Miss Advisor?
You are here on guild business, right?
Do you have time to spend talking to me?
I wanted to talk to you about that supporter of Bell-kun's.
You heard everything from that guy, did not you?
Find a good opportunity to escape, okay?
If only you had not met him...
No, this is the right thing to do.
One of those adventurers that I hate.
I may even get enough money to reach my goal.
I need money to leave the Familia, so...
You have screwed with me for too long, you goddamn prum!
Look at you, you little thief.
I thought you were going to be getting rid of that kid soon.
I figured if I laid a trap here, I would be sure to find you.
There are not a lot of paths you can use on this floor.
There are three more of us at the other routes.
But you came to see me!
You have even got a magic weapon!
You have been having a good time, have not you?
She even had a magic weapon!
Hey, so I wanted to ask you something...
You think you could leave all her stuff here?
D-Do you know what you are doing?
A dying killer ant will send out a signal to summon its fellows.
You do not want to end up a meal for them while you are fighting us, do you?
This looks pretty bad, does not it?
We are both part of the same Familia, right?
I will save you, so give me everything you have.
Or do you think you can fool me like yesterday?
This is a key to a gnome safe.
I converted the money to jewels and hid them there.
This looks pretty dire, does not it?
So you get to be our decoy.
But that was not the deal...
What kind of adventurer keeps a promise made to a supporter?
We do not need you anymore.
Keep supporting us till the end of your life, supporter!
This is why I hate adventurers.
But, I guess... this is what I deserve for deceiving Bell-sama, who was so nice to me.
If that is true, then maybe I should give up.
Why did you make me like this?
I hate myself for being so weak and small.
And nothing ever changes for me.
I wanted to be with someone.
The me who cannot do anything.
I will try to convince him, too.
Please tell Bell-kun to fire his supporter.
He is already made his decision.
No matter what happens, he will not abandon that supporter.
Goddess... even if that is true,
if she is in trouble, I want to help her.
Like I was before I met you!
I could not really see it in the fog,
but after you left another adventurer came, I guess,
and all the orcs around me disappeared.
So I was able to follow you quickly.
I am glad I made it in time.
Why are not you abandoning me?
Wait, do you not understand that I was tricking you?
Do you think I stole your knife as a joke?
I lied to you about how much money I got for trading in the magic stones!
Some days I got cocky and even made it 30-70!
And when you asked me to go pick up items,
I told you the items cost more than twice what they really did!
I have even said really mean things about you behind your back!
I am the worst kind of prum!
I have done nothing but lie to you!
Will you save any woman just because she is a woman?
Then it is because you are you.
I wanted to save you because you are you.
I did not want you to leave, because you are you.
I do not need another reason to save you.
Lili, if you are in trouble, talk to me.
I am an idiot, so I will not understand unless you say something.
It looks like I really had you worried.
As long as you are safe.
So what are you going to do now?
Are you looking for an adventurer?
But it is actually quite simple.
A rookie adventurer who wants the help of a supporter is advertising himself.
Will you go back into the dungeon with me, Lili?
I still was not able to apologize.
